  'iPhone and small Android users who want 30W USB-C PD fast charging on the go',
  'Minimalists who carry one small battery instead of a heavy 20000mAh brick',
  'AirPods and accessory owners who need Trickle-Charging Mode for small devices',
];
const notFor = [
  'Laptop owners — 30W is not enough to charge a MacBook meaningfully while in use',
  'Long-trip travelers who need more than two phone charges per day — get a 20000mAh bank',
  'Users with older USB-A cables only — there is no USB-A output port on this model',
